info:
Position Summary 


	NYU Shanghai is looking for interns, Facility Management.


	The intern will work with colleagues from Facility Management, providing a wonderful studying, teaching, and working environment for NYU Shanghai. We welcome those who have interests in developing skills in engineering projects and facilities operations, working in a Chinese–English bilingual environment, and building good communications with students, staff, and faculty.


	The intern will be responsible for assisting the team with engineering projects and helping the transition from the Century Avenue Campus to the Qiantan New Campus.





	Qualifications: 


	Currently working towards a Bachelors Degree.





	Required Knowledge, skills, and abilities: 





	Proficiency in English and Mandarin;


	Enthusiasm in working in a bilingual and multicultural environment;


	Be on duty at least 3 days a week;


	Detail-oriented and highly organized;


	Good teamwork spirit and skill;


	Proficiency in Microsoft Applications;


	Strong analytical and problem-solving skills;


	Willingness to explore new knowledge.





	Preferred Skills, Knowledge, and Abilities: 





	Good project management and multitasking skills;


	Basic knowledge of Computer-aided design (CAD);


	Basic knowledge of Building Automation (BA) systems;


	Familiar with Google Docs/app.

职责描述：
1、参与量化数据平台的设计和开发;
2、参与量化数据API接口的开发，金融数据模型标准化和处理;
3、参与数据服务体系搭建、优化与日常运行维护;

任职要求：
1、本科及以上学历，具有计算机、数学、统计学等相关专业背景优先;
2、熟练掌握Python开发以及Python相关技术栈；
3、熟悉Shell语言、Linux系统;
4、掌握常用的数据库(Mysql/Postgres/MongoDB)，有数据库编程经验;
5、高度的责任心；

加分项：
1、有金融数据平台开发经验，了解常用的金融数据；
2、了解时序数据库，如DolphinDB；
3、掌握C/C++者优先；
